    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> in the<strong> flour</strong>, tap off the excess, then add them into the <strong>speedy</strong> <strong>Marmite buttermilk</strong> and finally press them into the<strong> spice mix </strong>firmly to evenly coat all over – these are your <strong>Marmite coated chicken strips</strong></p>",
